	Device   "/dev/xxxx"  (where xxxx is the PS/2 mouse device)
</verb>
-->
<verb>
	Protocol "NetMousePS/2"
	Device   "/dev/xxxx"  (xxxx は PS/2 マウスデバイス)
</verb>

<!-- To use this mouse as the PS/2 device but the OS does not support PS/2 mouse 
